attributionInfo.brokerName: Better Homes and Gardens Real Estate - All Seasons

data.description: This lovely home in the heart of New London has so much to offer! The 3 bedroom 1 bath home is on a very large city lot (1.45 acres) on a pond and is adjacent to the Glacial Ridge Trail for year-round personal access to trail amenities. Convenient location- just a couple easy blocks to New London’s charming and historic downtown, schools, convenience stores, restaurants, swimming beach, brewery, shopping, bowling alley, boat launch, fishing, kayaking/canoeing, the Legion and much more. The private feel of the  backyard, the view of the pond, and the wildlife is amazing! Many interior and exterior updates including but not limited to newer windows, newer appliances, newer flooring, patio and pergola, and much more. Currently the main floor bedroom is being used as an added dining area. There is a lot of flexibility and potential in this home, the location is superb.
